PrecisOrder Respecting the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL of certain lands in the YUKON TERRITORY (WHITE RIVER FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of land in the Yukon Territory, in order to facilitate the settlement of native land claims, and (b) the repeal of Order in Council P.C. 1996-1870.
